### Health
GET http://localhost:8080/health

### Upload PDF
# Replace file path on your machine
# This requires an HTTP client that supports multipart file upload.
POST http://localhost:8080/upload/pdf/pdf
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./sample.pdf
------WebKitFormBoundary--

### Ask question
POST http://localhost:8080/qa/ask-question
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "document_id": "PUT_DOCUMENT_ID_HERE",
  "session_id": "optional-session-id",
  "question": "What does the document say about ...?"
}

